## Capability System

```python
if robot.has_capability("manipulation"):
    robot.pick_object("red bottle")
```

| Robot Type | Mobility | Navigation | Vision | Manipulation | Speech |
|-----------|----------|------------|--------|-------------|--------|
| Rover     | ✅       | ✅         | ✅     | ❌          | ❌     |
| Arm       | ❌       | ❌         | ✅     | ✅          | ❌     |
| Drone     | ✅       | ✅         | ✅     | ❌          | ❌     |
| Humanoid  | ✅       | ✅         | ✅     | ✅          | ✅     |

